
1. Six brief scenarios
  ✓ create: reaches workflow.proposed
  ✓ create: approve succeeds with version 1
  ✓ create: exactly one version written
  ✓ replace: proposes a Teams node via diff
  ✓ threshold filter: proposes filter.condition node
  ✓ weekday filter: proposes schedule.weekday_filter node
  ✓ explain: completes with streamed prose, no proposal
  ✓ why: completes with an explanation, no proposal

2. Five failure injections
  ✓ timeout: emits run.timeout
  ✓ fail: emits validation.error then run.failed
  ✓ fail: error code is VALIDATION_FAILED
  ✓ self-correct: emits validation.error, retry, then a valid workflow.proposed
  ✓ provider-switch: emits provider.switched then still proposes
  ✓ tool-failure: one tool.result ok:false, then succeeds and proposes

3. Approval gate edge cases
  ✓ reject: returns status rejected
  ✓ reject: writes zero versions
  ✓ double-reject: 400 VALIDATION_FAILED
  ✓ approve-after-reject: 400 (no pending proposal)
  ✓ approve: writes exactly one version
  ✓ double-approve: 400, no extra version written

4. Cancel mid-flight
  ✓ cancel: accepted
  ✓ cancel: run ends with run.cancelled, not run.completed

5. Reconnect / replay
  ✓ replay: got at least one event before disconnect
  ✓ replay: resumed stream has no duplicate seqs
  ✓ replay: resumed stream contains no events at/before the given Last-Event-ID

6. REST error / edge cases
  ✓ unknown conversation -> 404 CONVERSATION_NOT_FOUND
  ✓ unknown run -> 404 RUN_NOT_FOUND
  ✓ unknown workflow -> 404 WORKFLOW_NOT_FOUND
  ✓ empty message content -> 400 VALIDATION_FAILED
  ✓ diff missing from/to params -> 400
  ✓ node-definitions search returns matching catalog entries
  ✓ dev stripe-payment stub echoes amount/currency
  ✓ health check ok

TOTAL: 33 passed, 0 failed
